1
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:55,870
Xiao Chi,

2
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,240
if there were no more wars

3
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:01,230
at Tianlang Pass,

4
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,150
you could return to the capital

5
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,000
and stay with me and Fei Zheng

6
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,070
for years to come.

7
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,630
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

8
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:09,310
Chu,

9
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,400
Tianlang Pass

10
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,450
is Jinglan's most important pass.

11
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,079
For the nation and the people,

12
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,960
I will definitely defend it.

13
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,360
Only

14
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:23,800
for the nation?

15
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:27,030
Only for the people?

16
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,200
Your Majesty,

17
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,590
what Xiao Chi means is that

18
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,960
since you're the pillar of Jinglan,

19
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:40,079
protecting the people
is also protecting you.

20
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:41,280
Zheng is right.

21
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:42,750
I am defending

22
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,010
Tianlang Pass for you.

23
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:50,750
Appointing Fei Zheng
as the Minister of Rites

24
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,630
was indeed a wise move.

25
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,329
The Acupuncture Manual

26
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:59,829
seems to mention a way
to treat memory loss.

27
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:24,070
Neiguan regulates qi
and relaxes the tendons.

28
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,480
Neiguan…

29
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,930
Shenmen nourishes
the heart and calms the mind.

30
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,270
Shenmen...

31
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:43,950
Come, brothers,

32
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,409
let's have another drink.

33
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:58,680
Fei Zheng,

34
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,490
are you feeling unwell?

35
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,000
Your Majesty,

36
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:03,270
the weather

37
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,480
has turned colder

38
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,630
these past few days.

39
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,430
I’m afraid I’ve caught a chill.

40
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,680
A little rest should be enough.

41
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,830
Yes.

42
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:17,190
It's getting cold.

43
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,630
Zheng, then

44
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,990
you shouldn't go out for now.

45
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,560
Your Majesty,

46
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,580
you are absolutely right.

47
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,830
I really must finish

48
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:39,290
We should finish this last pot of wine.

49
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,390
I deserve it.

50
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,800
I deserve it.

51
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,070
Zheng,

52
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,480
your cold seems to have gotten worse.

53
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,600
Send for the Imperial Physician.

54
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,400
Your Majesty,

55
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,800
didn't I just say?

56
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,630
It’s only a chill.

57
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,340
Let's not bother anyone else.

58
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,890
Zheng, let me taste

59
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:18,430
what makes your wine

60
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,830
any different from mine?

61
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:22,290
I'll toast Your Majesty on his behalf.

62
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,430
That’s my good Third Brother.

63
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:31,870
Truly worthy of being Jinglan’s
great General Xiao.

64
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:32,680
Well,

65
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,830
I'll drink this pot.

66
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,680
You drink this one.

67
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,160
Your Majesty,

68
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,560
the three of us grew up together.

69
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,870
You know me best.

70
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,240
I'm impulsive

71
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:18,890
and prone to mistakes.

72
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,150
If I make a grave mistake,

73
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,390
Chu,

74
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,040
will you forgive me?

75
00:07:28,430 --> 00:07:29,750
Xiao Chi,

76
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,360
you've guarded
Tianlang Pass for so many years.

77
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,220
What mistakes could you make?

78
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,480
Since you returned to the capital,

79
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,610
you haven’t really come to see me much—

80
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,310
but

81
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,800
I know your nature.

82
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,480
Straightforward

83
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,850
and sincere.

84
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,140
What mistakes could you make?

85
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:49,870
What?

86
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,510
Could it be

87
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,270
you also want to kill me?

88
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,600
I would never.

89
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:06,800
If both of you want to harm me,

90
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,090
then in all of Jinglan,

91
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:13,240
there is truly no one I can trust.

92
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,720
Your Majesty.

93
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,040
Say no more.

94
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,070
I am

95
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,680
a bit tired,

96
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,280
and I've had enough to drink.

97
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:22,830
Chu!

98
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,270
We...

99
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,490
I have one more request.

100
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,549
Tell me.

101
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:37,669
Chu,

102
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,000
if...

103
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,080
Xiao Chi.

104
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,679
His Majesty is tired.

105
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,840
His Majesty needs to rest.

106
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,280
Your Majesty,

107
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,670
my body is truly failing me today.

108
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,000
I beg Your Majesty

109
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,030
to let me go back

110
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,150
alone.

111
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:01,840
All right.

112
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:03,670
Someone,

113
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:06,120
help Lord Fei

114
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,860
back to his residence.

115
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,280
Your Majesty,

116
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,670
I will take my leave.

117
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,440
Thank you for your hard work.

118
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,200
Sit down and talk.

119
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,220
Thank you, Chu.

120
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,000
I know what you are going to say.

121
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:54,440
The three of us

122
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,000
grew up together;

123
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,270
we’re like brothers.

124
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,910
You,

125
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,600
Fei Zheng,

126
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:05,200
will always be my closest.

127
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,320
Don't worry.

128
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,670
Even if you and Fei Zheng
commit a serious crime,

129
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,670
I will pardon you.

130
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,440
Chu,

131
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:18,560
are you serious?

132
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,870
Of course.

133
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,000
I am the Emperor.

134
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:27,240
The Emperor's word is his bond.

135
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:37,480
Baihui clears the mind
and sharpens the eyes.

136
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,270
Baihui?

137
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,150
You can't just carelessly
needle the Baihui acupoint.

138
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,480
It could go wrong.

139
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,550
Whatever.

140
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:48,610
Let's give it a try.

141
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,830
This river is so deep.

142
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,240
If you fall in,

143
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,480
we'll both die.

144
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,750
Then how should I thank Miss Han?

145
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:20,720
The best way to thank me

146
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,270
is to get well soon.

147
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,790
I will also go to battle,

148
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,150
defend the people of Jinglan—

149
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,550
and protect you as well.

150
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:43,240
Then, did you

151
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,360
forget any important friends
due to that?

152
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,630
How is that possible?

153
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:47,080
I...

154
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,360
Don't touch me!

155
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,510
It's me.

156
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,360
I'm Xiao Chi.

157
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:10,670
Aren't you afraid I might harm you?

158
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,200
If so, I'll return this life

159
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,240
to you.

160
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,440
Xiao Chi.

161
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:19,390
You are everyone's only hope now.

162
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,080
And,

163
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:24,280
I don't want anything
to happen to you either.

164
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:40,600
Xiao Chi!

165
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,890
Why are you here?

166
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:45,520
Where are you going?

167
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,400
To the palace.

168
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,230
When will you be back?

169
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,270
I'll be back as soon as I finish my work.

170
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:13,870
Come back soon.

171
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:18,510
Hurry up and go.

172
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,360
Okay.

173
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:26,030
Come back soon.

174
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,480
Greetings, Your Majesty.

175
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,750
Please rise.

176
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,150
Thank you, Your Majesty.

177
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,340
Did you drink too much last night?

178
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,440
I drank too much anyway.

179
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:51,000
It's the first time I've seen Fei Zheng

180
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,440
drink himself

181
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,030
into such an embarrassing state.

182
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,030
Lord Fei and I

183
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,760
naturally cannot compare to Your Majesty.

184
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,080
I asked you to come here today

185
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,170
to discuss something with you.

186
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,580
Your Highness,

187
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:08,200
have some grapes.

188
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:11,480
King of Mo specially
asked the envoys to bring these over.

189
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,010
He picked them all himself.

190
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,150
Are they not good?

191
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,370
They don't taste like they used to.

192
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:30,630
What's wrong?

193
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,670
Did something unpleasant happen

194
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:34,720
with the Emperor today?

195
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:39,910
Sit.

196
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,970
Liu Chu has changed.

197
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,810
He's become a stranger.

198
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,890
He wasn't like this before.

199
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:51,720
Ever since I was little, my father told me

200
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,720
I must love Liu Chu wholeheartedly,

201
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:55,790
and I did.

202
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:59,350
Day and night,
I imagined what he would be like.

203
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:02,280
I crossed mountains and rivers,

204
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:05,340
enduring injuries and hardship,
just to marry him.

205
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:07,570
I even became pregnant with his child,

206
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:09,350
planning to give birth to it.

207
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,630
What is all this for?

208
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:17,510
Maybe

209
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:20,630
this is what we have to endure.

210
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,390
This is fate.

211
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,300
Your Highness,

212
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:29,030
no matter what others do,

213
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,200
I will definitely stay by your side.

214
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,870
I hope this child

215
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:40,260
can bring Changmo and Jinglan

216
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:42,390
peace and tranquility.

217
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,080
Jin Xi,

218
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,390
you will always stay by my side,

219
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:57,240
right?

220
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,750
I will always be with you.

221
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:49,480
I heard

222
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:53,390
someone has been sneaking out of the palace
at night for secret meetings lately.

223
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:54,200
I want you

224
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,860
to thoroughly investigate this matter.

225
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,320
I wouldn't dare.

226
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,270
How dare I interfere

227
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,000
in palace affairs?

228
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,270
Chi,

229
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,870
besides you,

230
00:17:04,589 --> 00:17:06,440
there is no one I trust.

231
00:17:17,829 --> 00:17:19,430
The direction of the clinic?

232
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,829
Jin Xi?

233
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,270
Why are you here?

234
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:28,880
Han Mo has already been saved.

235
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,740
You should hurry back to Changmo.

236
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:32,960
Even though the two countries
are connected by marriage now

237
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,240
and it seems peaceful,

238
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,160
but...

239
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:39,160
Remember to protect yourself.

240
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:41,030
What are you talking about?

241
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,200
Aren't we doing fine now?

242
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:45,400
I just want you to be safe

243
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,750
and live happily.

244
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,030
Jin Xi.

245
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:51,880
Jin Xi!

246
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,790
What does this even mean?

247
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,680
Xiao Chi?

248
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:47,080
The poison has flared up again?

249
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,070
You're here.

250
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,440
This is already the second time.

251
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:56,000
Why didn't you
take the antidote I gave you?

252
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,030
I told you,

253
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,440
this antidote is for you.

254
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:00,750
Take it.

255
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,240
You must hold on.

256
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:05,760
Once Changmo invades Jinglan,

257
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:08,190
we will all get the antidote.

258
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:09,920
Then,

259
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,480
we will regain our freedom.

260
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:14,000
Gain freedom?

261
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,790
As spies,

262
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,850
you and I know too much.

263
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,790
Do you really think

264
00:19:22,590 --> 00:19:24,030
Meng Ling will let us go?

265
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,620
Let's not talk about this.

266
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:32,130
Hurry up and take the antidote first.

267
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:33,690
Don't worry.

268
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,200
I am highly skilled in martial arts.

269
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,460
I can definitely hold out until that day.

270
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,310
I'm fine.

271
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:53,790
Take it.

272
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,600
Once Prince Mo kills Liu Chu,

273
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:08,790
we can follow the Princess

274
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:10,250
back to Changmo together.

275
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,640
When that time comes,

276
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,590
we will find a free place,

277
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,800
and I will always be with you.

278
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:32,200
One is a brother

279
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:34,160
who has stayed by His Majesty’s side
for many years,

280
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:36,240
the other is the princess’s
female official—

281
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,400
yet both are spies.

282
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,160
How ironic.

283
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,880
To survive,

284
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,160
I must kill him.

285
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:50,880
Xiao Chi,

286
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,670
I was indeed sent by Changmo.

287
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,290
But after all these years,

288
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,960
you know what kind of person I am.

289
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:01,270
You know very well

290
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,480
how much I've done for Chu and Jinglan.

291
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,350
I know.

292
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:05,960
But so what?

293
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,350
Changmo has never given up

294
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:09,150
the idea of destroying Jinglan.

295
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:10,880
I am now poisoned by Gu

296
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:12,670
that flares up every day.

297
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:14,030
Even so,

298
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:15,920
I have never once thought of

299
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,480
betraying anyone.

300
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,740
Not reporting what you know is betrayal.

301
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:22,960
You even let spies stay around you.

302
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,530
That is also betrayal.

303
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:28,590
Fate really plays tricks on people.

304
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:30,270
But you know what?

305
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:33,030
We don't always have a choice in life.

306
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:36,160
But you chose

307
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,030
this path yourself.

308
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,480
There's no point in saying more.

309
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:42,270
Fei Zheng,

310
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:43,720
draw your sword.

311
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,550
Today,

312
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:47,270
you have to kill me

313
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:48,890
before leaving.【】

314
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:53,550
Fine.

315
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:56,030
For so many years,

316
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:58,400
we haven't fought.

317
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:00,480
Then today,

318
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,550
let me test

319
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:03,640
your swordsmanship, Chi.

320
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,880
Don't call me Chi.

321
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:42,880
Fei Zheng!

322
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:52,030
I can let you go,

323
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:54,610
but you must leave Jinglan immediately.

324
00:22:55,070 --> 00:22:55,600
Xiao Chi.

325
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:56,680
Say another word,

326
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,020
and I'll regret it.

327
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:00,440
All right.

328
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,270
Let's go.

329
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,480
Goodbye,

330
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,790
Zheng.

331
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:26,030
The Emperor has arrived!

332
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,680
Your Majesty.

333
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:44,300
You just let two spies
from Changmo go like that?

334
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,350
General Xiao,

335
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:52,110
tell me,

336
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:54,030
how should spies from Changmo

337
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,480
be dealt with

338
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,210
according to military law?

339
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:02,680
Your Majesty,

340
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,270
they should be
put in the Imperial Prison

341
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,870
and strictly interrogated.

342
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:07,880
Arrest them.

343
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,270
Chu.

344
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:10,750
Chu,

345
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,880
you promised me that

346
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,700
if Chu made a huge mistake,

347
00:24:14,030 --> 00:24:15,290
you would forgive him.

348
00:24:18,830 --> 00:24:20,310
Since I promised you,

349
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:23,200
I will definitely do it.

350
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,510
But facing

351
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:28,200
a spy from Changmo
who hid in Jinglan for years,

352
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:31,440
I have a lot to ask him.

353
00:24:32,270 --> 00:24:34,350
If he can confess everything,

354
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:37,440
I will surely keep my promise.

355
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:39,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

356
00:24:39,750 --> 00:24:40,830
As for her,

357
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:42,960
if she doesn't behave,

358
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:44,690
I can't guarantee her safety.

359
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,480
Your Majesty!

360
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:52,000
Your Majesty, please don't kill her.

361
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:52,830
You promised me

362
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:53,830
that since I saved your life,

363
00:24:53,830 --> 00:24:55,560
you would grant me one request.

364
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,750
Jin Xi is my childhood sister.

365
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,400
I beg you to spare her.

366
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,750
Please let her go.

367
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,080
I beg you, Your Majesty.

368
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:03,830
You two—

369
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:07,160
one wants to save his brother,

370
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,830
the other wants to save her sister.

371
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:10,680
Then what do

372
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,110
you take me for?

373
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:15,960
When have I ever not treated you
as my brothers,

374
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,680
as my family?

375
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:22,240
Changmo spies

376
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:24,200
are now disturbing the people of Jinglan

377
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,480
and waiting for a chance to kill me!

378
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,400
Whose side are you on now?

379
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,030
Chu.

380
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,070
But don't worry.

381
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:35,140
As long as they tell me
everything they know,

382
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:37,790
I won't make things difficult for them.

383
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:39,000
Fei Zheng, run!

384
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:41,340
I will never fall into your hands!

385
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,000
Jin Xi!

386
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,750
Jin Xi!

387
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:55,160
Jin Xi! Jin Xi!

388
00:25:55,350 --> 00:25:56,550
Why did you do this?

389
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:57,000
Jin Xi.

390
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:00,270
Fei Zheng.

391
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:01,750
We

392
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,480
can't

393
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:04,880
go back.

394
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,880
This is the best ending.

395
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:09,440
But

396
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:12,200
I'm so worried about you.

397
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:13,610
Physician Han,

398
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:15,030
your medical skills are exceptional.

399
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:15,960
Please save her.

400
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:16,790
I beg you.

401
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,830
Save her, please.

402
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,000
Yunling.

403
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,030
I'm here.

404
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:24,640
I...

405
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:29,030
I really miss our days

406
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,830
in Changmo.

407
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,160
Help me

408
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,030
hold on to them.

409
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:36,200
With my sister,

410
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,270
and you...

411
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,200
Yunling,

412
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,000
the Princess

413
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:46,400
is an innocent girl.

414
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,480
Please…

415
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:49,960
For my sake,

416
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:51,830
go into the palace

417
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,030
and take care of her.

418
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,680
I will.

419
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,030
I will.

420
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,200
Fei Zheng,

421
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:05,070
like me,

422
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,830
she never had

423
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:09,640
a choice.

424
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,350
Promise me.

425
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,750
Stay safe.

426
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:15,960
Don't worry.

427
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:17,830
I'm fine.

428
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:20,000
You'll be fine too.

429
00:27:21,030 --> 00:27:22,030
If

430
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,550
there is a next life,

431
00:27:25,350 --> 00:27:26,440
let’s

432
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:27,480
be

433
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,240
free

434
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,590
people.

435
00:27:32,790 --> 00:27:34,790
Okay.

436
00:27:37,590 --> 00:27:38,480
Jin Xi.

437
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,920
Jin Xi.

438
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,350
Go to sleep.

439
00:27:41,350 --> 00:27:42,030
Jin Xi.

440
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,160
Sleep well.

441
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,550
Jin Xi.

442
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,030
Jin Xi.

443
00:28:04,070 --> 00:28:05,870
I haven't allowed you to die yet!

444
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,160
Guards!

445
00:28:10,550 --> 00:28:12,480
Escort Fei Zheng to the Imperial Prison.

446
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,830
He is still my brother.

447
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:15,590
If anyone dares to harm him,

448
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:17,440
they will be severely punished!

449
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:21,190
Thank you, Your Majesty.

450
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:40,880
Jin Xi has been with me for seven years.

451
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,550
She is just a woman,

452
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,030
weak and delicate.

453
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:45,440
How could she be a spy?

454
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:51,550
Jin Xi and I have known each other
since we were young.

455
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:54,160
I only recently found out
she knows martial arts.

456
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,880
Was it really Liu Chu

457
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:58,000
who ordered Jin Xi's death?

458
00:28:58,590 --> 00:29:00,790
The Emperor had no choice.

459
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:03,300
The situation was urgent at the time.

460
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:13,160
Have you ever thought about

461
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,480
leaving here

462
00:29:14,750 --> 00:29:16,210
and returning to Changmo?

463
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:20,540
How can I get out of
this heavily guarded palace?

464
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:24,830
How can I return to Changmo?

465
00:29:25,790 --> 00:29:27,070
Even if I leave

466
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,880
and the marriage alliance is broken,

467
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:32,010
will the two countries go to war again?

468
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:33,350
I...

469
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:37,440
Are you still unable to move on from him?

470
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:43,070
He is the father of my child.

471
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,070
He is my husband.

472
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:49,550
He is the only man
I have ever loved in my life.

473
00:30:01,830 --> 00:30:03,480
If you want to leave here,

474
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:06,680
Xiao Chi and I will find a way
to help you.

475
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,570
I'm leaving now.

476
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,030
Wait.

477
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:22,070
Find a place with flowers,

478
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:23,480
grass, and trees

479
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,790
to bury Jin Xi.

480
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:28,830
Don't worry.

481
00:30:29,310 --> 00:30:30,960
Jin Xi is also my friend.

482
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:33,290
I’ll see her off properly.

483
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:38,030
Take care.
